headline: Arthur J. Gallagher (AJG) Q4 Earnings and Revenues Beat Estimates
summary: Arthur J. Gallagher (AJG) delivered earnings and revenue surprises of +1.28% and +0.31%, respectively, for the quarter ended December 2025. Do the numbers hold clues to what lies ahead for the stock?

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher (NYSE:AJG) Exceeds Q4 CY2025 Expectations
summary: Insurance brokerage firm Arthur J. Gallagher (NYSE:AJG) reported Q4 CY2025 results topping the market’s revenue expectations, with sales up 35.6% year on year to $3.63 billion. Its non-GAAP profit of $2.38 per share was 1.4% above analysts’ consensus estimates.

headline: Arthur J. Gallagher: Q4 Earnings Snapshot
summary: ROLLING MEADOWS, Ill. AP) — Arthur J. Gallagher & Co. (AJG) on Thursday reported fourth-quarter net income of $151 million. On a per-share basis, the Rolling Meadows, Illinois-based company said it had net income of 58 cents.
